`1.1.0'
=E2=95=8C=E2=95=8C=E2=95=8C=E2=95=8C=E2=95=8C=E2=95=8C=E2=95=8C

  =E2=80=A2 A first support for `flycheck' ([#29], [#33] and [#37])
  =E2=80=A2 Use a more efficient way to ensure that a vector is empty ([#27=
])
  =E2=80=A2 Made the mode-line "lighter" more conventional ([#26])


