<div id=3D"outline-container-org3662d3c" class=3D"outline-3">
<h3 id=3D"org3662d3c">Etienne Marais announced</h3>
<div class=3D"outline-text-3" id=3D"text-org3662d3c">
<p>
We are happy to announce the release of Dune <code>3.18.1</code> :camel:=20
</p>

<p>
This version is a minor release that contains a bug fix to an issue that wa=
s preventing <code>pkg-config</code> from finding some libraries in some co=
ntexts.
</p>

<p>
If you encounter a problem with this release, you can report it on the <a h=
ref=3D"https://github.com/ocaml/dune/issues">ocaml/dune</a> repository.
</p>
